@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_pnidzz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((0.23 * 0.27) * v0)
    v1 = wp.abs((wp.abs(tmp + 0.97) - wp.exp(v2 + 0.02)))
    v0 = ((wp.exp(v0 + 0.84) - 0.61) - (v1 / v1))
    v0 = wp.exp(v2)
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.abs(v1 + 0.21)) * v0)
    v0 = wp.cos(0.95)
    data[tid] = v0
